到新竹可以來用餐～\",\"time\":1747743156,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"鄭壯志\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117818583020305490055/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZbXb9x-vaGdV29T8usc0VZ1qtrV7Xt1_CALLmbyrqHpXKoVvs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 週前\",\"text\":\"CP值很高的燒肉店👍\\n推薦雪花牛、松阪豬、透抽、厚切牛舌🎉\\n甜點是紫米紅豆粥加一分🥣\\n吃到滿滿的幸福感🎊\",\"time\":1746779467,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"陳小萱\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102920450829076656169/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW__tAiAMrz73wq_upbbOfMOrpKFjCLcAIqMMeDb-FgcZE0rco=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 個月前\",\"text\":\"服務生很勤勞換烤網，餐點品質中規中矩，高湯很清淡，線上點餐操作容易，套餐份量也很足夠。使用炭火燒烤，偶爾會回來吃個氛圍感。少一顆星是因為沒有壽星生日優惠⋯\",\"time\":1741355337,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"sam liu\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109898001552008622299/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxaqKefuaDCeDY7VEqx0mB_J4J49MTBsHSZZ1bt_Oyd2dgLuU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":1,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 個月前\",\"text\":\"我們來吃晚餐！\\n可是再來的機會幾乎是渺茫。\\n我叫了四次生菜要包燒肉\\n只來了一次\\n感覺他們就只是送肉，然後再來就是趕緊收盤子\\n中間段隔了一個很大的空間\\n需要人提醒他才檢查我們的單子\\n才又開始送餐品\\n新橋燒肉在新竹名氣很大\\n有一點點感覺他們的肉現在品質沒那麼好\\n以前是吃過新竹的，另一間分店、\\n也吃過竹北店\\n以前吃的都不會覺得如此的差\\n可是這次讓我感覺的如此的不好\\n，燒肉店這麼多，不去了\",\"time\":1738243304,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNTAt-4jeab4txrEcHZzIKRUi1gKVIMNBNHjQFnz-DVceczpAs10jpf_knx5XlTMzNPYUx8vGdqzI7mcgTAvj5xfI385Ap4W0ychTV_jrMSk43SWGG_BHZa3M2n0TNR2mEVpAtuLvfu230hE9of8bnvH9oTkCFsVzhxyvFBZg26C6gDmOOemckO7GMbkJA5HtMj-96KsUllB632tsLmMqc71w19h2BOO0Wpuwz5abJucqL8C0nn3lkYwktSWF-_bVcPyRtmmkQ-Vds75cckXgc9z5F72RMtyqaFXAf91nWLUES4EPYgUmmD91Z6AxMMCeV6VVMeVga0\",\"AXQCQNSUtqEozWzoNKYuLw3uWMf00gftr0BTlqaxtjAIcYv5kvF3j